# 🚀 EliteLance – Freelancing Marketplace

EliteLance is a role-based freelancing platform built using Django, where clients can post jobs, freelancers can apply, and managers can monitor platform activity.

---

## 🌟 Features

### 👤 Role-Based System
- Client → Post and manage jobs
- Freelancer → Browse jobs and submit proposals
- Manager → Monitor platform stats and activity

---

### 💼 Job & Proposal System
- Clients can create, update, and delete jobs
- Freelancers can apply with proposals
- Proposal status: Pending / Accepted / Rejected

---

### 📊 Dashboards
- Client Dashboard → Job stats & proposals
- Freelancer Dashboard → Proposals & contracts
- Manager Dashboard → Platform analytics

---

### 🔌 API (Django REST Framework)
- `/api/jobs/` → Public job listings
- `/api/proposals/` → Authenticated user proposals

---

### 🎨 UI
- Modern UI with Tailwind CSS
- Aurora background & glassmorphism design
- Responsive layout

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- Backend: Django
- API: Django REST Framework
- Database: SQLite
- Frontend: HTML, Tailwind CSS
- Version Control: Git & GitHub

---

